{"tid":1364053,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗飲食及購物指南","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:22:47.000Z","uid":16740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6263e618d3e94dbb74c84b1cf2f28857a00ad4b2","tid":1364053,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"作為一個係元朗土生土長既牛屎仔<br />\n今日想推廣一下元朗既好去處，美食及購物地點<br />\n<br />\n首先，中秋即將來臨，相信好多香港人都想食到好食既月餅，小弟現推介恆香月餅，恆香既月餅比市面上既好好多，好有月餅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟最高紀錄一次過食撚左兩盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地址係元朗大棠路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxSdiJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxSdiJy.png&h=46d1f803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二間就係元朗人必食既爽爽醉雞豬扒店，一定要食新鮮雞！好撚滑！豬扒又係好撚有豬扒味，諗起都想食番一打<br />\n地址係YOHO 附近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGC8R4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGC8R4y.png&h=4babde94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後食飽梗係要行下啦，唔通個個都變到肥絲大隻咁撚肥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現推介sell hk旗下既YOHO Mall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYoHo mall位處於YOHO<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRYv5qm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRYv5qm.png&h=b9efa6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位入黎元朗可以食得開心，買得稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e81807bd5e8891e395056014d16fa801ddc948d","tid":1364053,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"大家好好享受元朗既美食及購物體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665207dfa6d5d9d23f5568aff37abd6c9d333c03","tid":1364053,"uid":16740